extendedInfo.description: Dog Kind is a classic elimination game.Players make conversion between each other icon by clicking the icon even as three or more bricks to eliminate,then get the score.An icon for each additional 5 points to eliminate, to the corresponding points can pass.Player can swap icon Up or down, left or right, diagonal.Hope you like this software.

reviews.title: Dogs too small
reviews.comment: This is unplayable as the dogs are far too tiny - you can barely see them!
reviews.author: Angie Dominic
